"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12761184-aau-junior-olympics-track-and-field-2024-results-on-day-8\", \"text\": \"Adidas Indoor Nationals  Texas Distance Festival  Chandler Rotary Invite  W&L Outdoor T&F Carnival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  Corsair Classic  The AAU Junior Olympics have officially wrapped up.  Over 13,000 athletes traveled to the games in Greensboro, NC with 11 finals across all age groups happening on the last day of events.  The 2024 Junior Olympics Track and Field competition isstreaming live on FloTrack, MileSplit and the FloSports app.Highlights, replays and breaking news are on both platforms.  Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.  Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.  Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.  \\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\"}"